															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610252574" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;" >Decibelles</a></span> <span class="odate time_1428456994 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">08 Apr 2015 01:36</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2266237">
									

<p>I hope you enjoy this slice-of-life tale about a girl going through her birthday! <span style="font-size:5%;">im being totally sjw-y guys :3</span> I've used her before in <a href="/so-it-was">a</a> few <a href="/scp-1848">other</a> places <a href="/decibelle-author-page">here</a>.</p>
<p>Thank you to TwistedGears, thedeadlymoose, Cimmerian, LordSpy, AndarielHalo (for looking and letting me use <a href="/scp-2277">SCP-2277</a>), Light, Tuomey, and God knows who else I ran this by. As always, feel free to correct for spelling/grammar issues. If your edit is wrong, I can change back, no biggie.</p>
<p>I also referenced a bunch of songs in here, as well as a tale. Some are pretty obvious. Can you catch them?</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Here&nbsp;they&nbsp;are&nbsp;anyway.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Here&nbsp;they&nbsp;are&nbsp;anyway.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p>All of Me Wants All of You (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Se6-q57xJCg">Sufjan Stevens - All of Me Wants All of You</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;The Beatles… well, Paul McCartney rather, recorded one of their most seminal songs, and released it 48 years ago today.&quot; (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2WQAl5nJWHs">The Beatles - Yesterday</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;&quot;You're not old enough to hit your mid-life crisis&quot; (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FoQIuDEHVng">Faith No More - Midlife Crisis</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>10:30&#160;A.M.</strong>, shark-branded cigarette (<a href="/10-30-a-m">10:30 A.M.</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Hey you, you got a cigarette?&quot; &quot;You know I know that you got one on you.&quot; (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yf6FOrG1wYA">Gospel - Golden Dawn</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;How does it feeeeeel?<br />
How does it feel?<br />
To be on yooourrr ooown?<br />
With no direction hooome?<br />
A complete unknoown?<br />
Like a rooolling stone? (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=syNLBJ_Lq9E">Bob Dylan - Like a Rolling Stone</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Haaappy biiirthday, baabyyyy yeah…<br />
You make me feel bluuuuue…<br />
Swollen eyes worth since you left…<br />
Haaappy biiirthday, baabyyyy yeah&#8230;&quot; (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mrGoGsP4f5Q">Shudder to Think - No Rm. Kentucky 9</a>)</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
